    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="32e59-102">Essa classe é usada como parte de um <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrameCollection> em conjunto com um <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorAnimationUsingKeyFrames> para animar uma <xref:System.Windows.Media.Color> valor da propriedade ao longo de um conjunto de quadros-chave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32e59-102">This class is used as part of a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrameCollection> in conjunction with a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorAnimationUsingKeyFrames> to animate a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Color> property value along a set of key frames.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="32e59-103">Um quadro-chave define um segmento do <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorAnimationUsingKeyFrames> ao qual ela pertence.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32e59-103">A key frame defines a segment of the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorAnimationUsingKeyFrames> to which it belongs.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="32e59-104">Cada quadro chave tem um destino <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame.Value%2A> e um <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame.KeyTime%2A>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32e59-104">Each key frame has a target <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame.Value%2A> and a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame.KeyTime%2A>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="32e59-105">O <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame.KeyTime%2A> Especifica a hora em que o quadro chave <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame.Value%2A> devem ser atingido.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32e59-105">The <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame.KeyTime%2A> specifies the time at which the key frame's <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame.Value%2A> should be reached.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="32e59-106">Um quadro chave anima do valor de destino de quadro chave anterior a seu próprio valor de destino.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32e59-106">A key frame animates from the target value of the previous key frame to its own target value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="32e59-107">Ele começa quando o quadro chave anterior termina e termina quando é atingido sua própria chave de tempo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32e59-107">It starts when the previous key frame ends and ends when its own key time is reached.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="32e59-108">Quadros chave discretos como <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DiscreteColorKeyFrame> criar "saltos" repentinos entre valores (sem interpolação).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32e59-108">Discrete key frames like <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DiscreteColorKeyFrame> create sudden "jumps" between values (no Interpolation).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="32e59-109">Em outras palavras, a propriedade animada não altera até que o tempo de chave do quadro chave seja atingido no ponto em que a propriedade animada repentinamente vai para o valor de destino.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32e59-109">In other words, the animated property does not change until the key frame's key time is reached at which point the animated property goes suddenly to the target value.</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
